definition: to furnish/to provide/supply (as in supply and demand)
to/for/for the benefit of/to give/to allow/to do sth (for sb)/(grammatical equivalent of 被)/(grammatical equivalent of 把)/(sentence intensifier)

sentences.english: Oil-free compressors of course, are the logical choice for instrument-air supplies.
sentences.chinese: 自然，無油壓縮機必然被選擇爲儀用空氣供給者。

sentences.english: To keep a fresh supply take one or two cloves from each bulb and replant them.
sentences.chinese: 保持新鮮供給要花一至兩丁香每個燈泡和補種。

sentences.english: Health promotion activities conducted by health providers are not enough.
sentences.chinese: 醫療服務供給方健康促進工作不夠。

sentences.english: We can only supply you with 20000 yards of pure silk.
sentences.chinese: 咱們只能供給二萬碼的僞絲綢。

sentences.english: In the experimental group, zinc sulfate was given intramuscularly each day, beginning 2 days before operation.
sentences.chinese: 供鋅組於手術前2天起經肌肉供給硫酸鋅。

sentences.english: We define the Water Deposit Supply Function and the Water Loan Demand Function.
sentences.chinese: 並定義水市場中的存水供給函數及貸水需求函數。

sentences.english: The trolley bus picks up current from an overhead wire.
sentences.chinese: 電車的電能是通過架空線供給的。

sentences.english: Which Cylon sabotages the Galactica's water supply in the aptly named "Water"?

sentences.english: Such variations in food supply have several causes.
sentences.chinese: 這種在食物供給方面的變化有幾個原因。

sentences.english: We strengthened regulation and oversight of thereal estatemarket to improve the mix of market housing available.
sentences.chinese: 加強房地產市場調控和監管，着力調整住房供給結構。

sentences.english: Both plants and animals supply these natural materials.
sentences.chinese: 植物與動物都供給這些天然材料。

sentences.english: We will ensure an adequate supply of agricultural products and increase farmers’ incomes through multiple channels.
sentences.chinese: 確保農產品供給，多渠道增加農民收入。

sentences.english: According to the traditional concepts , government is the sole suppler of public goods .

sentences.english: Children depend on their parents for food and cloth.
sentences.chinese: 孩子們依賴父母供給衣食。

sentences.english: Because of this, all types of supplies were scarce.
sentences.chinese: 因爲這些原因，所有的供給都比較緊張。
